metadata.description:
Coaltoons are aliens from another planet who come back to Earth in search of their fellow Coaltoons who crashed on July 7, 1947 in Roswell, NM and never heard from again.

  • This is the very first original Coaltoons NFT art.
  • This collectible Coaltoons art is digitized from a hand printed 3D Coaltoons Necklace that I incorporated with an original drawing designed specifically for Coaltoons by the very talented Phoebe Sugo from Sugo Studio.
  • The original 1 of 1 hand 3D printed Coaltoons Necklace that is associated with this Coaltoons NFT will be shipped to the buyer of this NFT.
  • This Coaltoons NFT is 1 of 1 because no two Coaltoons Necklaces that I 3D hand print that is accompanying this digitized art is able to be duplicated.
  • The Coaltoons Necklaces that accompany any future Coaltoons NFT's are only created at the pace in which I am able to hand 3D print them at. So if you like a specific Coaltoons Necklace that accompanies the NFT, then first come first serve.
  • Buyer will unlock the full resolution 3,000px X 3,000px Coaltoons collectible art and of course get their Coaltoons Necklace shipped to them.
